158
00:07:40,170 --> 00:07:43,000
I'm glad you're helping each other.

159
00:07:43,920 --> 00:07:45,170
However, Fang Chao,

160
00:07:45,560 --> 00:07:48,090
I hope you can think independently.

161
00:07:48,320 --> 00:07:49,560
Use your brain.

162
00:07:50,290 --> 00:07:53,410
1500 meters is a long distance
with many variables.

163
00:07:53,880 --> 00:07:56,210
It requires you to be more flexible.

164
00:07:56,530 --> 00:07:58,290
You can't count on others
to tell you what to do

165
00:07:58,290 --> 00:08:00,050
