167
00:08:05,000 --> 00:08:06,050
Got it, coach.

168
00:08:07,850 --> 00:08:08,690
Okay.

169
00:08:09,320 --> 00:08:10,650
Think about it.

170
00:08:12,320 --> 00:08:13,290
Bye, coach.

171
00:08:36,890 --> 00:08:37,730
What's wrong?

172
00:08:41,920 --> 00:08:43,130
Listen,

173
00:08:43,890 --> 00:08:44,890
I don't need you

174
00:08:44,890 --> 00:08:46,130
to help me with tactics anymore.

175
00:08:48,010 --> 00:08:49,370
Why are you avoiding me?

176
00:08:50,680 --> 00:08:52,320
At least we're teammates.

177
00:08:53,200 --> 00:08:55,010
Are you going to change
the order of relay?

178
00:08:57,170 --> 00:08:58,490
It's possible.

179
00:09:01,890 --> 00:09:03,530
Do we have to end up like this?

180
00:09:05,890 --> 00:09:07,250
I'm saying this one last time.

181
00:09:08,200 --> 00:09:11,170
I want to handle it myself.

182
00:09:12,530 --> 00:09:14,410
I admit I'm not as smart

183
00:09:14,490 --> 00:09:15,650
as you,

184
00:09:16,720 --> 00:09:18,840
but I want to count on myself.

185
00:09:20,410 --> 00:09:22,010
I think you're overthinking it.

186
00:09:23,080 --> 00:09:24,170
If you didn't know

187
00:09:24,200 --> 00:09:25,770
I was the one who helped you,

188
00:09:27,200 --> 00:09:28,650
you wouldn't overthink it, right?

189
00:09:28,840 --> 00:09:29,720
Yes.

190
00:09:32,920 --> 00:09:34,080
I can accept help

191
00:09:35,560 --> 00:09:37,960
from anyone except you.

192
00:09:43,960 --> 00:09:44,800
Fine.

193
00:09:46,530 --> 00:09:47,370
I'll apologize.

194
00:09:47,440 --> 00:09:48,560
No need.

195
00:09:51,170 --> 00:09:53,600
Neither Lin Ge nor you

196
00:09:55,680 --> 00:09:57,200
owe me anything.

197
00:09:58,490 --> 00:09:59,410
It's not your fault.

198
00:10:02,920 --> 00:10:04,200
But I'm sad.

199
00:10:09,800 --> 00:10:10,770
It's not my fault either.

200
