Wei, you're 500m.

203
00:10:34,410 --> 00:10:36,320
- We're both 500m.
- We both got in.

204
00:10:37,250 --> 00:10:38,200
I'll tell him.

205
00:10:38,200 --> 00:10:39,040
Okay.

