207
00:10:40,440 --> 00:10:41,600
We all got singles.

208
00:10:42,050 --> 00:10:42,890
I'm 500m.

209
00:10:42,960 --> 00:10:44,080
You're 500m and 1000m.

210
00:10:44,080 --> 00:10:45,080
Fang Chao is 1500m.

211
00:10:45,290 --> 00:10:46,130
What about me?

212
00:10:48,010 --> 00:10:50,050
Sorry, I didn't notice.

213
00:10:52,490 --> 00:10:54,080
It's okay.
Seven Gold, let's take a look.

214
00:10:54,080 --> 00:10:54,920
Let's go.

215
00:10:58,440 --> 00:10:59,650
Still angry?

216
00:11:00,650 --> 00:11:01,490
It takes time.

217
00:11:01,720 --> 00:11:02,840
Focus on the competition.

218
00:11:03,720 --> 00:11:05,530
This Youth Championship is different.

219
00:11:06,010 --> 00:11:07,250
No senior teammates.

220
00:11:07,530 --> 00:11:08,920
So, I can skate as fast as I want

221
00:11:09,170 --> 00:11:10,600
instead of covering for others, right?

222
00:11:11,920 --> 00:11:12,890
Go back to training.

223
00:11:26,920 --> 00:11:27,920
Mr. Li is talking to

224
00:11:27,920 --> 00:11:28,920
different event groups.

225
00:11:29,560 --> 00:11:30,960
I think it's about the tactics.

226
00:11:32,650 --> 00:11:33,650
As for the tactics,

227
00:11:33,920 --> 00:11:35,680
don't overthink it.

228
00:11:35,720 --> 00:11:36,680
Just take it easy.

229
00:11:37,840 --> 00:11:38,960
I'm not like you.

230
00:11:39,050 --> 00:11:40,410
I'm so nervous.

231
00:11:41,130 --> 00:11:43,680
Right now, we need to relax

232
00:11:43,680 --> 00:11:44,770
and clear our minds.

233
00:11:47,410 --> 00:11:49,080
Okay. Ask them over.

234
00:11:57,130 --> 00:12:00,560
Mr. Li wants to talk to you.

235
00:12:02,200 --> 00:12:03,440
- Let's go.
- Let's go.

236
00:12:09,290 --> 00:12:10,130
- Coach.
- Coach.

237
00:12:10,920 --> 00:12:12,680
Are you nervous about the competition?

238
00:12:13,010 --> 00:12:13,850
No.

239
00:12:14,080 --> 00:12:15,490
No. I'm excited.

240
00:12:15,800 --> 00:12:16,840
It's good,

241
00:12:17,200 --> 00:12:19,440
but don't be too excited.

242
00:12:20,410 --> 00:12:22,770
You need to adjust yourself gradually.

243
00:12:22,890 --> 00:12:25,290
Save your greatest passion
for the competition.

244
00:12:25,890 --> 00:12:26,730
Got it.

245
00:12:26,740 --> 00:12:29,250
With your ability,
unless you make mistakes,

246
00:12:29,290 --> 00:12:30,890
you'll get into the final.

247
00:12:31,410 --> 00:12:33,770
So, I'm going to tell you

248
00:12:33,770 --> 00:12:35,410
the tactics of the final.

249
00:12:35,840 --> 00:12:38,290
Lin Ge, you have a great responsibility.

250
00:12:38,800 --> 00:12:42,130
You need to cover for Xie Lingwei
in the final.

251
00:12:50,560 --> 00:12:52,370
I know you care about this competition.

252
00:12:53,410 --> 00:12:54,600
Since the Huarong Cup,

253
00:12:55,200 --> 00:12:56,530
you've worked hard for half a year

254
00:12:57,010 --> 00:12:58,490
because you want to prove yourself

255
00:12:58,600 --> 00:12:59,520
in this competition.

256
00:13:00,320 --> 00:13:02,320
It's obvious that I'm not as good

257
00:13:02,320 --> 00:13:03,170
as Wei.

258
00:13:03,550 --> 00:13:04,770
She'll be the core

259
00:13:04,770 --> 00:13:06,130
of our cooperation.

260
00:13:08,010 --> 00:13:09,320
You've figured it out.

261
00:13:09,650 --> 00:13:10,720
Why are you so upset?

262
00:13:12,010 --> 00:13:13,560
I don't want
to cover for others forever.

263
00:13:14,050 --> 00:13:15,840
This time, all the participants
are our peers,

264
00:13:15,840 --> 00:13:16,680
no seniors.

265
00:13:17,720 --> 00:13:18,650
I thought

266
00:13:18,650 --> 00:13:20,290
Mr. Li would let us fight for ourselves,

267
00:13:20,680 --> 00:13:22,960
but it turns out
I still need to cover for Wei.

268
00:13:24,960 --> 00:13:26,050
It occurred to me

269
00:13:26,050 --> 00:13:27,920
that Zhu Zhu once told me

270
00:13:28,050 --> 00:13:30,320
even if I'm a fast horse,

271
00:13:30,600 --> 00:13:31,490
I'll meet

272
00:13:31,490 --> 00:13:32,840
a faster leopard.

273
00:13:33,960 --> 00:13:34,960
I used to think she was

274
00:13:34,960 --> 00:13:36,490
trying to make an excuse
for her mistakes.

275
00:13:37,200 --> 00:13:38,530
Now I finally understand.

276
00:13:40,050 --> 00:13:41,010
Understand what?

277
00:13:42,490 --> 00:13:44,320
I understand why she hated me

278
00:13:44,890 --> 00:13:46,370
and why she was so desperate.

279
00:13:49,410 --> 00:13:50,320
But don't worry.

280
00:13:50,530 --> 00:13:51,770
I won't lose control.

281
00:13:53,490 --> 00:13:55,250
Do you remember I asked you
to compete with her

282
00:13:55,250 --> 00:13:56,890
before joining the provincial team?

283
00:14:00,440 --> 00:14:01,800
You can't join us unless it's

284
00:14:01,800 --> 00:14:02,840
less than 48 seconds.

285
00:14:06,490 --> 00:14:08,170
Lin Ge, the second place,

