00:14:08,440 --> 00:14:09,530
47.97 seconds.

287
00:14:10,960 --> 00:14:13,200
Only when competing with stronger people
can you be faster.

288
00:14:15,050 --> 00:14:16,840
Lin Ge, don't be upset.

289
00:14:17,600 --> 00:14:19,080
Even if we have a late start,

290
00:14:19,490 --> 00:14:21,440
we will find our places.

291
00:14:21,890 --> 00:14:23,290
I'll be with you.

292
00:14:25,530 --> 00:14:26,370
Okay.

293
00:14:26,770 --> 00:14:28,320
I haven't competed for a long time.

294
00:14:28,650 --> 00:14:29,720
Let's finish it first.

295
00:14:32,010 --> 00:14:32,850
For our dreams.

296
00:14:33,840 --> 00:14:34,680
We can make it.

297
00:14:37,800 --> 00:14:39,800
Men's 500m Final

298
00:14:39,800 --> 00:14:41,320
has reached the last stage.

299
00:14:41,320 --> 00:14:42,490
The participants are very close.

300
00:14:42,490 --> 00:14:43,560
Nie Chi is leading the race.

301
00:14:43,560 --> 00:14:44,850
He crossed the line!

302
00:14:45,600 --> 00:14:47,320
We're looking at the Women's 500m Final.

303
00:14:47,320 --> 00:14:49,410
Lin Ge has guarded the way
for Xie Lingwei.

304
00:14:49,410 --> 00:14:50,720
The genius girl Xie Lingwei

305
00:14:50,800 --> 00:14:52,170
is leading the race.

306
00:14:52,770 --> 00:14:53,650
Sprint!

307
00:14:53,650 --> 00:14:54,650
She won!

308
00:14:57,410 --> 00:14:59,250
Let's talk after the press conference.

309
00:15:02,080 --> 00:15:02,920
What's wrong?

310
00:15:03,370 --> 00:15:04,680
So many people.

311
00:15:06,530 --> 00:15:08,410
You're world champions.

312
00:15:08,410 --> 00:15:09,250
Why are you scared?

313
00:15:09,650 --> 00:15:12,170
Don't be nervous on the stage. Let's go.

314
00:15:13,100 --> 00:15:17,820
(World Youth Short Track Speed Skating
Championship Press Conference)

315
00:15:27,490 --> 00:15:29,770
The press conference
has officially begun.

316
00:15:29,890 --> 00:15:31,130
Reporters, please ask questions.

317
00:15:33,370 --> 00:15:34,210
Mr. Li,

318
00:15:34,530 --> 00:15:36,530
are you satisfied with the results?

319
00:15:36,890 --> 00:15:37,730
First of all,

320
00:15:37,800 --> 00:15:38,960
dear press friends,

321
00:15:38,960 --> 00:15:41,650
thank you for your concern and support.

322
00:15:41,890 --> 00:15:42,960
As we know,

323
00:15:43,370 --> 00:15:45,960
the national team
has the best short track

324
00:15:46,600 --> 00:15:47,960
- Well done.
- speed skaters.

325
00:15:48,800 --> 00:15:49,640
So,

326
00:15:49,910 --> 00:15:50,890
I'm satisfied.

327
00:15:51,960 --> 00:15:53,800
You secured the second place

328
00:15:53,800 --> 00:15:54,800
the whole time,

329
00:15:54,800 --> 00:15:57,130
the person behind you couldn't pass you.

330
00:15:57,560 --> 00:15:59,440
She nearly passed me in the curves.

331
00:15:59,530 --> 00:16:00,860
They're strong opponents.

332
00:16:00,860 --> 00:16:02,550
They're both...

333
00:16:02,720 --> 00:16:03,800
Mr. Li is ridiculous.

334
00:16:04,130 --> 00:16:05,050
Silver medal is amazing.

335
00:16:05,370 --> 00:16:06,920
Why can't you go on the stage?

336
00:16:08,080 --> 00:16:09,050
Don't say that.

337
00:16:09,370 --> 00:16:10,600
As for Xie Lingwei,

338
00:16:10,600 --> 00:16:12,200
she's got the best endurance

339
00:16:12,490 --> 00:16:13,490
and concentration.

340
00:16:13,770 --> 00:16:16,370
Therefore, we told her to lead the race

341
00:16:16,370 --> 00:16:17,770
the whole time.

342
00:16:17,920 --> 00:16:19,320
Okay. Thanks, Mr. Li.

343
00:16:20,010 --> 00:16:20,850
Hello, Wei.

344
00:16:21,200 --> 00:16:22,040
You broke

345
00:16:22,050 --> 00:16:23,960
the Youth Championship record of 500m.

346
00:16:24,250 --> 00:16:25,600
How do you feel now?

347
00:16:26,800 --> 00:16:29,080
(Xie Lingwei)
Happy and nervous.

348
00:16:29,490 --> 00:16:30,560
Mr. Li said

349
00:16:30,720 --> 00:16:32,890
your tactic was to lead the race.

350
00:16:33,080 --> 00:16:34,170
What's your opinion?

351
00:16:34,490 --> 00:16:36,650
If I lead the race,

352
00:16:36,650 --> 00:16:37,920
they can't affect me,

353
00:16:38,010 --> 00:16:39,920
and that's safer.

354
00:16:40,080 --> 00:16:42,770
Weren't you worried
that they might pass you?

355
00:16:50,720 --> 00:16:51,560
No.

356
00:16:51,920 --> 00:16:52,760
Why?

357
00:16:52,890 --> 00:16:54,050
Because I'm the fastest.

358
00:16:54,890 --> 00:16:55,800
Okay. Thanks.

359
00:16:56,050 --> 00:16:57,050
How could she say that?

360
00:16:57,770 --> 00:16:59,490
If you hadn't covered for her,

361
00:16:59,560 --> 00:17:01,170
would she have won so easily?

362
00:17:01,290 --> 00:17:03,010
Now that she's won the gold medal,

363
00:17:03,170 --> 00:17:04,600
shouldn't she thank you?

364
00:17:05,210 --> 00:17:06,210
- Stop.
- Any questions?

365
00:17:06,320 --> 00:17:08,500
- Wei is a simple girl.
- Okay. This one.

366
00:17:10,250 --> 00:17:12,770
Nie Chi, this is also
your first Youth Championship,

367
00:17:12,770 --> 00:17:14,560
and you won the Men's 500m.

368
00:17:14,690 --> 00:17:16,360
Is there anything you want to say?

369
00:17:17,820 --> 00:17:21,760
(Nie Chi)

370
00:17:21,770 --> 00:17:22,800
I want to thank someone.

371
00:17:23,360 --> 00:17:24,200
Who?

372
00:17:26,320 --> 00:17:28,840
The person who's been there for me.

373
00:17:50,080 --> 00:17:50,920
Okay.

374
00:17:51,050 --> 00:17:52,120
Oh, no, Lin Ge.

375
00:17:52,120 --> 00:17:53,690
I can't find my colorful rope.

376
00:17:54,640 --> 00:17:55,560
It's missing?

377
00:17:55,560 --> 00:17:58,210
Yes. When I left the stage,

378
00:17:58,210 --> 00:18:00,010
it disappeared from my hand.

379
00:18:00,490 --> 00:18:02,500
You can't race without it?

380
00:18:02,600 --> 00:18:04,120
My grandma gave it to me

381
00:18:04,120 --> 00:18:05,450
to protect me.

382
00:18:05,640 --> 00:18:07,210
If I don't wear it in competitions,

383
00:18:07,210 --> 00:18:08,880
I'll definitely get injured.

384
00:18:09,730 --> 00:18:10,880
What should I do?

385
00:18:10,880 --> 00:18:11,930
Oh my god. I...

386
00:18:11,930 --> 00:18:13,160
Look, what's this?

387
00:18:13,600 --> 00:18:14,840
You found it.

388
00:18:15,010 --> 00:18:16,400
Do you know where I found it?

389
00:18:16,730 --> 00:18:18,770
- No.
- It slipped from your pocket.

390
00:18:19,320 --> 00:18:20,290
Put it on.

391
00:18:20,970 --> 00:18:22,160
You're so careless.

392
00:18:22,160 --> 00:18:23,010
Amazing.

393
00:18:23,620 --> 00:18:24,490
Thank god you're here.

394
00:18:24,490 --> 00:18:26,400
I'm important at moments like this,
right?

395
00:18:26,400 --> 00:18:27,820
You're always important.

396
00:18:28,560 --> 00:18:30,320
- Wei. Take a photo.
- Let me see.

397
00:18:30,450 --> 00:18:31,840
Okay. I have to go.

398
00:18:31,840 --> 00:18:32,680
Go.

399
00:18:35,160 --> 00:18:37,210
Well, closer, closer.

400
00:18:37,320 --> 00:18:38,160
Good.

401
00:18:38,930 --> 00:18:39,770
Come on.

402
00:18:40,400 --> 00:18:41,240
Smile.

403
00:18:41,880 --> 00:18:43,160
Very good.

404
00:18:44,160 --> 00:18:45,010
Champions,

405
00:18:45,010 --> 00:18:46,490
please raise your gold medals.

406
00:18:46,490 --> 00:18:47,330
Go on.

407
00:18:48,530 --> 00:18:49,370
Lin Ge.

408
00:18:49,490 --> 00:18:50,500
- Coach.
- Look at me.

409
00:18:50,770 --> 00:18:53,210
That was great cooperation.

410
00:18:53,560 --> 00:18:54,400
Thanks, Coach.

411
00:18:54,450 --> 00:18:56,290
But I noticed you were exhausted

412
00:18:56,290 --> 00:18:57,800
in the last lap,

413
00:18:57,800 --> 00:18:58,930
and they nearly passed you.

414
00:19:00,490 --> 00:19:02,560
You need to do more physical training.

415
00:19:05,560 --> 00:19:06,800
Keep it up.

416
00:19:07,690 --> 00:19:08,530
Got it.

417
00:19:15,800 --> 00:19:16,880
Okay. Champions,

418
00:19:16,880 --> 00:19:18,450
please show me your medals.

419
00:19:20,160 --> 00:19:21,450
Yes, closer.

420
00:19:36,900 --> 00:19:40,260
(World Youth Short Track Speed Skating
Championship, Women's 500m, Silver Medal)

421
00:19:44,900 --> 00:19:46,360
(Honorary Champions)
Wei, I'll help you.

422
00:19:46,370 --> 00:19:47,210
No need.

423
00:19:47,210 --> 00:19:48,320
It's okay. I have strength.

424
00:19:48,690 --> 00:19:49,530
Give me.

425
00:19:49,530 --> 00:19:50,370
Okay.

426
00:19:52,640 --> 00:19:54,010
I've been too busy

427
00:19:54,250 --> 00:19:55,320
to talk to you.

428
00:19:55,690 --> 00:19:56,640
Let's hang out.

429
00:19:57,600 --> 00:19:59,080
I want to take a nap.

430
00:19:59,640 --> 00:20:01,400
Wei didn't feel well last night,

431
00:20:01,530 --> 00:20:03,560
so I got up twice
to get hot water for her.

432
00:20:05,400 --> 00:20:06,360
Then see you later.

433
00:20:06,610 --> 00:20:07,450
Okay.

434
00:20:07,490 --> 00:20:09,800
Lin Ge, I forget my key.

435
00:20:09,930 --> 00:20:10,770
Coming.

436
00:20:16,400 --> 00:20:17,400
You should be together.

437
00:20:17,400 --> 00:20:18,600
They say you're a good match.

438
00:20:18,600 --> 00:20:19,800
Exactly.

439
00:20:20,640 --> 00:20:22,080
- Stop.
- Look. Here it is.

440
00:20:22,160 --> 00:20:23,730
- So weird.
- Exactly.

441
00:20:24,530 --> 00:20:25,970
The comments say they're a good match.

442
00:20:25,970 --> 00:20:27,320
You're all here.

443
00:20:28,400 --> 00:20:29,770
What are you talking about?

444
00:20:29,930 --> 00:20:30,840
You're awake.

445
00:20:31,530 --> 00:20:33,880
Several official media accounts

446
00:20:33,880 --> 00:20:35,840
just posted the photos
of Wei and Nie Chi,

447
00:20:36,010 --> 00:20:37,770
and there are so many comments.

448
00:20:37,770 --> 00:20:38,640
They say

449
00:20:38,640 --> 00:20:40,800
they're the official couple
of the national team.

450
00:20:42,080 --> 00:20:42,920
Look.

451
00:20:44,530 --> 00:20:46,210
So many comments.

452
00:20:46,210 --> 00:20:47,880
(I've finally become a man
who deserves you.)

453
00:20:47,880 --> 00:20:48,880
(Champion couple.)
Go ahead.

454
00:20:48,880 --> 00:20:50,400
It's really wild.

455
00:20:50,690 --> 00:20:51,970
They even wrote a novel

456
00:20:51,970 --> 00:20:52,930
in the comments.

457
00:20:53,400 --> 00:20:54,250
Nie Chi

458
00:20:54,250 --> 00:20:56,320
worked hard to stand on the same stage

459
00:20:56,530 --> 00:20:57,840
with Wei.

460
00:20:57,840 --> 00:20:58,930
He finally won the gold medal.

461
00:20:59,530 --> 00:21:02,770
I've finally become a man
who deserves you.

462
00:21:08,930 --> 00:21:09,840
They're

463
00:21:11,120 --> 00:21:13,290
talking nonsense, huh?

464
00:21:14,290 --> 00:21:15,320
They're just joking.

465
00:21:15,530 --> 00:21:16,640
They'll forget it very soon.

466
00:21:16,840 --> 00:21:17,730
Don't take it seriously.

467
00:21:18,450 --> 00:21:19,800
It's not like that.

468
00:21:20,770 --> 00:21:22,210
I'm worried that if Xie Lingwei sees

469
00:21:22,210 --> 00:21:23,400
too many comments,

470
00:21:23,970 --> 00:21:25,880
she'll have feelings for Nie Chi.

471
00:21:26,490 --> 00:21:28,210
It'll be a mess.

472
00:21:28,840 --> 00:21:30,770
What are they talking about?

473
00:21:31,050 --> 00:21:32,640
It's a wrong matchmaking.

474
00:21:32,770 --> 00:21:34,770
Nie Chi's closest friend is Lin Ge.

475
00:21:35,120 --> 00:21:36,010
You don't know.

476
00:21:36,250 --> 00:21:37,560
Maybe he learned from

477
00:21:37,560 --> 00:21:39,450
Jin Xinxin's mistakes,

478
00:21:39,620 --> 00:21:41,560
and he wants to use Lin Ge to get Wei.

479
00:21:41,880 --> 00:21:42,800
It's not like that.

480
00:21:42,930 --> 00:21:44,730
There's nothing between us.

481
00:21:44,730 --> 00:21:46,080
Stop saying that.

482
00:21:47,120 --> 00:21:49,930
Lin Ge, are you Nie Chi's girlfriend?

483
00:21:55,970 --> 00:21:59,970
So, everything is possible.

484
00:22:00,120 --> 00:22:02,600
Besides, they're both
young and successful.

485
00:22:02,600 --> 00:22:03,690
What a good match.

486
00:22:04,210 --> 00:22:05,640
Wei, don't you agree?

487
00:22:06,730 --> 00:22:07,570
I...

488
00:22:09,690 --> 00:22:11,800
I don't know.

489
00:22:11,880 --> 00:22:13,530
Which means it's possible.

490
00:22:14,080 --> 00:22:14,920
Let me ask you,

491
00:22:14,990 --> 00:22:16,250
who's more handsome,

492
00:22:16,250 --> 00:22:17,200
Jin Xinxin or Nie Chi?

493
00:22:21,010 --> 00:22:22,050
Nie Chi.

494
00:22:22,560 --> 00:22:23,840
Among the boys in the men's team,

495
00:22:23,840 --> 00:22:25,640
who will you watch a movie with?

496
00:22:29,450 --> 00:22:30,450
Nie Chi.

497
00:22:30,880 --> 00:22:32,450
Who do you want to receive

498
00:22:32,450 --> 00:22:33,730
milk tea from?

499
00:22:34,880 --> 00:22:37,530
Maybe Nie Chi.

500
00:22:37,560 --> 00:22:39,840
So, you like him.

501
00:22:41,320 --> 00:22:42,160
What?

502
00:22:44,290 --> 00:22:45,690
Those involved are often confused.

503
00:22:45,690 --> 00:22:46,600
Lin Ge,

504
00:22:46,840 --> 00:22:48,880
are you really not
in a relationship with him?

505
00:22:49,400 --> 00:22:52,250
Yes, you like him.

506
00:22:53,290 --> 00:22:54,560
- Don't be embarrassed.
- Exactly.

507
00:22:54,560 --> 00:22:55,530
Not a big deal.

508
00:22:55,970 --> 00:22:57,400
I'm hungry. Let's eat something.

509
00:22:57,540 --> 00:22:58,510
- She's blushing.
- Yes.

510
00:22:58,880 --> 00:23:00,400
- No. I'm not hungry.
- Tell me more.

511
00:23:00,600 --> 00:23:01,560
Let's go.

512
00:23:03,050 --> 00:23:05,120
Jinting, I want to take a walk alone.

513
00:23:05,490 --> 00:23:07,840
The netizens know what's going on.

514
00:23:07,970 --> 00:23:09,250
You're the only one

515
00:23:09,250 --> 00:23:10,600
who hasn't realized it.

516
00:23:10,610 --> 00:23:11,880
- Stop kidding.
- Exactly.

517
00:23:14,050 --> 00:23:15,970
Nie Chi, talk to Lin Ge.

518
00:23:20,530 --> 00:23:23,490
(Is it tragic to be in the same era)

519
00:23:23,490 --> 00:23:25,320
(with a genius athlete?)

520
00:23:25,730 --> 00:23:28,730
(Is it more tragic to be
in the same era)

521
00:23:29,160 --> 00:23:30,360
(with her)

522
00:23:30,530 --> 00:23:32,120
(and refuse to give up?)

523
00:23:32,640 --> 00:23:36,080
(Now I finally understand
why Zhu Zhu was indifferent.)

524
00:23:36,800 --> 00:23:38,690
(If we're meant to be opponents,)

525
00:23:39,160 --> 00:23:41,560
(we shouldn't make friends
in the first place.)

526
00:23:42,290 --> 00:23:44,120
(But no one has ever told me)

527
00:23:44,120 --> 00:23:48,080
(how to solve it
when we're already friends.)

528
00:23:49,120 --> 00:23:50,600
Jinting said you were upset.

529
00:23:51,530 --> 00:23:52,370
What's wrong?

530
00:23:52,930 --> 00:23:54,880
Is it because they made fun of

531
00:23:54,880 --> 00:23:55,770
Xie Lingwei and me?

532
00:23:57,560 --> 00:23:59,400
I have no feelings for her.

533
00:23:59,880 --> 00:24:01,600
But everyone thinks

534
00:24:01,840 --> 00:24:03,690
she deserves you
because she won the gold medal.

535
00:24:04,320 --> 00:24:06,510
But what's that got to do with me?

536
00:24:06,800 --> 00:24:07,990
I only like you.

537
00:24:08,560 --> 00:24:11,120
I don't even deserve
to stand beside you.

538
00:24:11,120 --> 00:24:12,970
You don't need the gold medal
to stand beside me.

539
00:24:13,080 --> 00:24:14,370
You don't understand!

540
00:24:15,010 --> 00:24:17,120
I've finally realized this.

541
00:24:17,730 --> 00:24:19,450
You deserve someone better than me,

542
00:24:21,120 --> 00:24:24,290
whether it's family background
or financial capacity.

543
00:24:25,250 --> 00:24:27,320
I won a silver medal,

544
00:24:27,800 --> 00:24:29,530
but compared to your gold medals,

545
00:24:30,490 --> 00:24:32,600
I'm just a loser.

546
00:24:35,490 --> 00:24:38,730
Lin Ge, don't look down on yourself.

547
00:24:39,080 --> 00:24:40,160
I believe one day,

548
00:24:40,160 --> 00:24:42,050
you'll win the gold medal.

549
00:24:42,050 --> 00:24:43,450
One day?

550
00:24:45,730 --> 00:24:47,880
When will it happen?

551
00:24:54,010 --> 00:24:54,850
Lin Ge,

552
00:24:56,600 --> 00:24:58,730
I can't tell you the exact date.

553
00:24:59,290 --> 00:25:01,040
But I believe you,
and you have to believe

554
00:25:01,290 --> 00:25:02,770
the day will eventually come,

555
00:25:03,690 --> 00:25:04,880
because you're Lin Ge.

556
00:25:05,120 --> 00:25:06,290
Your competitive spirit

557
00:25:06,290 --> 00:25:08,120
will lead you to success.

558
00:25:14,400 --> 00:25:16,400
Can you wait for me?

559
00:25:17,880 --> 00:25:19,360
I want to stand beside you

560
00:25:20,400 --> 00:25:21,770
with a gold medal.

561
00:25:22,400 --> 00:25:23,400
I don't want to wait.

562
00:25:26,530 --> 00:25:27,450
Let's tell them.

563
00:25:28,290 --> 00:25:29,130
Let's tell

564
00:25:29,450 --> 00:25:30,290
everyone

565
00:25:30,290 --> 00:25:32,120
we're together, okay?

566
00:25:33,560 --> 00:25:34,450
Are you trying

567
00:25:36,360 --> 00:25:38,160
to reassure me?

568
00:25:51,530 --> 00:25:53,490
I just want everyone to know

569
00:25:54,600 --> 00:25:55,840
you're my girlfriend.

570
00:26:12,450 --> 00:26:14,930
